<figureCitation id="13402A7CFF92E478A92551E540B4FC42" box="[343,439,906,931]" captionStart="FIGURES 133–143" captionStartId="115.[151,264,1660,1683]" captionTargetBox="[151,1437,193,1639]" captionTargetId="figure@115.[151,1437,193,1639]" captionTargetPageId="115" captionText="FIGURES 133–143. leaf mines; 133: Liriomyza arctii Spencer in Ƒerbesina alternifolia; 134: L. asclepiadis Spencer in Asclepias exaltata; 135: L. baccharidis Spencer in Erigeron annuus, lower surface (left) and upper surface (right); 136: L. blechi Spencer in Plantago virginica; 137: L. brassicae (Riley) in Lepidium virginicum; 138: L. eupatoriella Spencer in Ageratina altissima; 139: L. eupatoriella in Ƒernonia baldwinii; 140: L. eupatorii (Kaltenbach) in Baccharis halimifolia; 141: L. fricki Spencer in Trifolium repens; 142: L. galiivora (Spencer) in Galium circaezans (transmitted light); 143: L. ivorcutleri spec. nov. in Silphium perfoliatum." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1452947/files/figure.png" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Fig. 143</figureCitation>
