<figureCitation id="13402A7CFF92E478A92451BD40ABFC0A" box="[342,424,978,1003]" captionStart="FIGURE 30–34" captionStartId="103.[151,250,1661,1683]" captionTargetBox="[151,1437,217,1639]" captionTargetId="figure@103.[151,1437,193,1639]" captionTargetPageId="103" captionText="FIGURE 30–34. Figure 30: Liriomyza eupatorii (Kaltenbach), puparia. Figures 31–32: L. ivorcutleri spec. nov.; 31: puparium, 32: adult male. Figures 33–34: L. valerianivora spec. nov.; 33: puparia; 34: adult female." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1452923/files/figure.png" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Fig. 31</figureCitation>
